      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you may find some minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with careful use. The interior is tidy and comfortable, with all major features functioning properly. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road.",
