    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a living masterpiece that defies the passage of time. This isn't merely a vehicle; it is a preserved breath of history, gleaming with a luster that captures every sunset and commands every gaze. The interior is a sensory sanctuary, where the scent of high-grade leather remains as potent and inviting as the day it was crafted. Every switch click and engine hum whispers of a life spent in climate-controlled adoration, untouched by the common elements. To pilot this machine is to experience the pinnacle of its lineage\u2014a rare chance to own a soul-stirring icon that feels as though it was delivered from the showroom only yesterday.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly superlative condition. This specimen has been preserved to an exacting standard, featuring a flawless finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous care, ensuring a driving experience that is as mechanically sound as it is visually stunning. For the buyer who accepts no compromises, this vehicle stands as a benchmark of quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 48500.0,
