    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and it still smells like the day it rolled off the lot. It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape; you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find even a tiny blemish on this showroom-quality ride. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look and let\u2019s chat!",
      "price": 48500.0,
