    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted, showroom-caliber performance machine. This unit features a blueprinted powerplant with reinforced internals and a high-flow induction system for optimal volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a precision-calibrated limited-slip differential and a dual-clutch gearbox with zero-latency shifts. Every bushing has been inspected for structural integrity, and the geometry is dialed for peak turn-in response. This isn't just a car; it's a high-tolerance instrument of speed, maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. Turn-key and ready for the canyon or the circuit.",
